source.name: FY 10 Education Recipients by State
source.description: FY 10 Education Recipients by State. The data represents the number of individuals by VA education program who have used their VA education benefit during fiscal year 2010. State statistics may include individuals who used their education benefits in more than one state, therefore the total within this table may be different than the  total number of beneficiaries during the fiscal year.
